  mso-no-proof:yes'>Caguar Fur is the luxuriant fur of the striped Caguar.<=
o:p></o:p></span></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>The Caguar is a huge sabre-cat that prowls the wild
  rainforests of Marshy Swamp worlds. The adult length of a Caguar from nos=
e to
  tail is approximately 4 meters. They have razor-sharp claws that they use=
 to
  capture their prey.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
